videos.description: Reid Travis rises up to grab a rebound, then lays in an easy bucket vs. Tennessee State.
videos.headline: Travis leaps for rebound, makes putback layup

videos.description: Tennessee State's Donte Fitzpatrick-Dorsey lobs an alley-oop to Emmanuel Egbuta, who throws it down and adds a free throw.
videos.headline: Tennessee State's Egbuta slams down alley-oop

videos.description: Kentucky freshman Immanuel Quickley dribbles around a screen and sinks a 3-pointer to extend the Wildcats' lead over Tennessee State.
videos.headline: Quickley pulls up to drain 3-pointer

videos.description: Kentucky runs in transition and Keldon Johnson takes it to the hoop for a nifty layup vs. Tennessee State.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Johnson scoops in transition layup

videos.description: Nick Richards catches an alley-oop pass from Ashton Hagans and jams it with two hands late in the 2nd half vs. Tennessee State.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Richards throws down alley-oop pass
